{"tid":697111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"納瓦羅警告：中興通訊若再違規　將被三振出局　將會關門","createTime":"2018-06-10T16:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T18:02:40.000Z","uid":147314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"764e9492feec11375562c92c05195dc2014ae19e","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:31:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1013133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1013133&d=7dik%2B57InS7eQz7adFhe%2FcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b86e6c12\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1013133</a><br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅警告中興通訊若再違規將被三振出局<br />\n<br />\n10.06.2018 23:46<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅警告中國電訊設備生產商中興通訊，如果再做不當的事，將會在美國停業。納瓦羅接受霍士電視台訪問時指，<span style=\"color: red;\">若中興再次出事，就會被三振出局，將會關門，總統特朗普在事件上展現善意，給了「人情」國家主席習近平。</span><br />\n<br />\n華府日前與中興簽署原則性協議，解除禁止中興採購美國零部件7年的命令，容許中興恢復業務。中興需支付10億美元罰款，另將4億美元交由第三方託管，若日後再違規就會被徵收。中興亦要在30日內改組董事會及管理層，並要讓美方挑選的合規團隊進駐公司。"},{"pid":"5397c0146f4ed1fb0f81582298aef7b06399376e","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201806100235-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201806100235-1.aspx&d=7dik%2B57InS7eQz7adFhe%2FcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=338f8e13\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201806100235-1.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，納瓦洛（Peter Navarro ）告訴福斯廣播公司（Fox）：「中興這件事將採三振出局方式。如果他們再出事，就將被停業。（川普）總統是作了個人情給中國國家主席，以展現善意。」"},{"pid":"a576d5bc85c574912b9339f5159533409d7e9da9","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"Navarro 都咁講，中興呢邊應該暫時無事"},{"pid":"fc1edcb02c3628dc361fb2d2411df103cf81e275","tid":697111,"uid":14918,