<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79c67cd4a9304fe980d324b7fdd3cac8f06be5c","tid":697111,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"174e915ec2ba2fdb61330ffb193fa714a36086b9","tid":697111,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc1edcb02c3628dc361fb2d2411df103cf81e275","tid":697111,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"黨委搞事算唔算違規"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"黨委大定監察組大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"要人大釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5883bbc80ae9e580c6ef0fe5abd79f1fb26eb1d5","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d559d69aa7426ae69ecc5094251ffbcbe78d6d6","tid":697111,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a576d5bc85c574912b9339f5159533409d7e9da9","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"Navarro 都咁講，中興呢邊應該暫時無事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"但係依家好似中興又有其他野衰左調查緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知會唔會咁都算三振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通一交多1b又即刻收皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:23:39.000Z","msg":"咁絕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6484bd20fa58477db2e91b02cd8a8292fd15068","tid":697111,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:24:47.000Z","msg":"係中國人就有應畀d骨氣執左佢<br />\n咁樣受洋人玩"},{"pid":"701c45863b7d63ce3b69c8186efdcebccee743c7","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f38b4802b57eff37c12b883f3e4cb736e083803","tid":697111,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66a9c09e59e65ee906ff2983ffb1ad9c89d2709c","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"即係唔洗佢死住係有原因"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"金仔加有單收購deal俾中國攔住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:33:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180607/1186393.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180607%2F1186393.htm&d=7dik%2B57InS7eQz7adFhe%2FcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ce353f20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180607/1186393.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報：陸準備批准高通收購恩智浦<br />\n<br />\n2018年06月07日 22:56<br />\n<br />\n美國晶片製造廠高通(Qualcomm)對荷蘭恩智浦半導體公司(NXP)的收購案出現進展。根據《華爾街日報》報導，一位知情人士表示，中國準備批准高通和恩智浦的交易，過去幾天大陸監管機構一直和高通的法律團隊溝通，針對「技術細節」進行協商。<br />\n<br />\n高通併購恩智浦剛好碰到中美貿易戰，進而連動到中國批准的速度。隨著貿易磋商緩和，美國商務部長7日表示，已經和中國電信設備商中興通訊(ZTE)達成協議，向中興開罰10億美元（約新台幣297.3億元），美方會派監管團隊進入該公司內部監察，還要求在託管帳戶內存入4億美元（約新台幣118.9億元），並撤換管理層和董事會全體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3123/3123664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3123%2F3123664.jpg&h=f1bbaf0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，高通和恩智浦的併購案一直和中美貿易戰有密切關聯。一開始美國商務部於4月16日宣布，禁止美國公司向中興通訊銷售電子技術或通訊元件7年；中國商務部立刻在19日做出反擊表示，正在審查高通和恩智浦的併購案，可能會對市場產生負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n但其實在5月13日時，中美雙方就互相釋放善意，中國監管機構稱已重啟對高通收購恩智浦一案，恢復因貿易戰而停滯的審核工作。同天美國總統川普也在推特發文，願意讓中興通訊恢復營運，因為中國已流失太多工作崗位，已指示商務部完成這項工作。<br />\n<br />\n直到中國國務院副總理劉鶴率團赴美磋商後，雙方於5月20日發表聯合聲明宣布停止貿易戰，同意增加美國農產品和能源的出口，美方日後也將派團至中國討論具體事項。<br />\n<br />\n至於計劃以440億美元（約新台幣1.31兆元）收購恩智浦的高通，目前已獲得美國、俄羅斯、歐盟、韓國等8個監管機構批准，僅剩中國商務部未做出決定。這將是半導體行業歷史上規模最大的一筆交易，能讓高通成為快速增長汽車晶片市場的領頭羊。"},{"pid":"6b784fc60c0ba79faf92df73bea689210e1430dd","tid":697111,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:35:37.000Z","msg":"Fool me twice , shame on me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e08baeb8737c49cbfa3a40538751583f981da2","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f38b4802b57eff37c12b883f3e4cb736e083803","tid":697111,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66a9c09e59e65ee906ff2983ffb1ad9c89d2709c","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"即係唔洗佢死住係有原因"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"金仔加有單收購deal俾中國攔住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"唔知中國批幾耐"},{"pid":"3f7d36e28174e9059f709780c9145d563f96e762","tid":697111,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d94509fa580806aa725564521e19577b8719fc44","tid":697111,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}